# Backend API Design

# REST APIs

## Clusters

```http
GET /api/clusters
```

## Namespaces

```http
GET /api/namespaces?clusterId=xxx
```

## Pods

```http
GET /api/pods?namespace=default
```

## Containers

```http
GET /api/containers?pod=nginx
```

## Files

```http
GET /api/files?path=/app
```

## Download File

```http
GET /api/download?path=/app/file.txt
```

## Upload File

```http
POST /api/upload
```

## Delete File

```http
DELETE /api/file?path=/tmp/test.txt
```

